A '''Haitian Bahamian''' {{lang-fr|Haïtien Bahamian}}, {{lang-ht|Ayisyen Bahamian}}) is a [[The Bahamas|Bahamian]] resident or citizen of full or partial [[Haiti]]an ancestry. Most of whom are illegally residing in the country. The Bahamas currently does not allow dual citizenship, so those who are Bahamian citizens, must renounce their Haitian citizenship. 

